  "2026-07-01T08:04:10.045Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: implemented CodeFactor complexity remediation for update/register-mutation. Removed target complexity suppressions, added register-mutation schema repeatable alias/role coverage, and manually smoke-tested installed pm in /tmp/tmp.3bglbDFU7O with custom status aliases, custom type, runtime schema field CLI flags, create/update/list/health. Gates: linked pm test run passed all 4 commands under tracker context (coverage 100/100/100/100, focused update/register tests, contracts check, lint/static quality); direct pnpm typecheck, pnpm build, pnpm contracts:check, pnpm lint, pnpm changelog:pm:check, secrets scan, pnpm audit, pm health summary, git diff --check passed. GitHub: no open PRs/issues, no Dependabot/code-scanning alerts, latest Auto Release 28499297083 success on 2026-07-01T06:52:39Z. Sentry: issue list reachable; sampled unresolved PM-CLI-16 and PM-CLI-1Q are stale with lastSeen 2026-06-13, not new current-regression evidence; telemetry status enabled with last successful flush 2026-07-01T08:03:07.606Z. pm validate strict-exit still reports pre-existing closed-item resolution metadata warnings, but command references and history drift are clean."
