  "2026-07-01T08:29:51.374Z",claude-code-agent,"Greptile follow-up review 3df1cc5f-6934-4d13-b26e-4a26ea2dea8a found two P2 behavior-preservation concerns. Fixed both before push: restored defensive string-to-array coercion for programmatic schema alias/role option inputs in register-mutation, and changed replace-tests helper behavior so an empty defensive replacement uses the existing empty-array cleanup path instead of assigning undefined. Added focused register-command coverage for the programmatic string coercion path. Verification after fixes: unsuppressed ESLint for update/register/test files passed; pnpm typecheck passed; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/commands/update-command.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/register-commands.spec.ts passed (175 tests); node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed 262 files / 5265 tests with Statements 100%, Branches 100%, Functions 100%, Lines 100%."
