  "2026-07-01T09:06:34.568Z",claude-code-agent,"CodeRabbit PR #413 review follow-up: verified thread-aware review data and fixed all still-valid comments. Moved canceled-status assignee cleanup after ownership mutations and records assignee in changed_fields; made runtime schema field set/unset conflicts explicit and taught update command option-policy presence to resolve runtime unset fields with the runtime registry; replaced the register-command test's private Commander _actionHandler access with the public parseAsync path while retaining defensive string coercion coverage. Verification so far: unsuppressed ESLint for changed update/register tests passed; pnpm typecheck passed; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/commands/update-command.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/register-commands.spec.ts passed (176 tests); node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed 262 files / 5266 tests with 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines."
